instructions:
Execute the following exactly:

=== MILESTONE 2.5 ===
1. Modify `src/layouts/EngineLayout.astro`:
- Add `interface Props { title?: string; description?: string; pageType?: 'standard' | 'transactional' | 'immersive' | 'content' | 'catalog'; }`
- Destructure `pageType = 'standard'` and pass it to `<BaseLayout>`.
2. Modify `src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro`:
- Add the same `pageType` prop interface.
- Wrap `<PopupModal />` with `{pageType !== 'transactional' && pageType !== 'catalog' && <PopupModal />}`
- Wrap `<AnnouncementBar />` with `{pageType !== 'transactional' && <AnnouncementBar />}`
3. Apply `pageType` to all `src/pages/**/*.astro` files:
- `/checkout/razorpay.astro` -> `pageType="transactional"`
- `/index.astro`, `/about.astro`, `/contact.astro` -> `pageType="immersive"`
- `/blog.astro`, `/blog/[slug].astro` -> `pageType="content"`
- `/shop/`, `/collections/`, `/lookbooks/`, `/products/` pages -> `pageType="catalog"`

=== MILESTONE 3 ===
1. Run `npm install @keystatic/core @keystatic/astro`
2. In `astro.config.mjs`, import `keystatic` and add `keystatic()` to `integrations` BEFORE `alpinejs()`. Add `output: 'hybrid'` in config if not already set, needed for Keystatic.
3. Create `keystatic.config.ts`:
```typescript
import { config, fields, collection, singleton } from '@keystatic/core';

const brandId = process.env.PUBLIC_BRAND_ID || 'zelia-vance';

export default config({
  storage: { kind: 'local' },
  collections: {
    products: collection({
      label: 'Products',
      slugField: 'title',
      path: `src/content/${brandId}/products/*`,
      format: { data: 'frontmatter', content: 'none' },
      schema: {
        title: fields.slug({ name: { label: 'Title' } }),
        sku: fields.text({ label: 'SKU' }),
        price: fields.number({ label: 'Price' }),
        image: fields.text({ label: 'Image URL' })
      }
    }),
    blog: collection({
      label: 'Blog',
      slugField: 'title',
      path: `src/content/${brandId}/blog/*`,
      format: { contentField: 'content' },
      schema: {
        title: fields.slug({ name: { label: 'Title' } }),
        excerpt: fields.text({ label: 'Excerpt', multiline: true }),
        publishDate: fields.date({ label: 'Publish Date' }),
        content: fields.mdx({ label: 'Content' })
      }
    })
  },
  singletons: {
    settings: singleton({
      label: 'Site Settings',
      path: `src/content/${brandId}/settings/site`,
      format: { data: 'yaml' },
      schema: {
        name: fields.text({ label: 'Brand Name' }),
        tagline: fields.text({ label: 'Tagline' }),
        monetization: fields.object({
          show_ads: fields.checkbox({ label: 'Show Ads on Blog' })
        })
      }
    })
  }
});
```
(Note: Keystatic schema keeps basic scaffold, missing fields act as standard markdown).
